3": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010924, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par salaam ho, ay Wali'e Khuda. Aap par salaam ho, ay Hujjat'e Khuda. Aap par salaam ho, ay zameen ki taarikiyyo’n mein Khuda ke noor. Salaam ho aap par, woh jin ki shaan Khuda ne zaahir farmaayi. Aap ki ziyarat ko aaya hu, aap ke haq se waaqif, aap ke dushmano ka dushman, aap ke dosto’n ka dost. Pas meri shafa’at kare apne Rab ke huzoor ay mere Aaqa.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے ولی خدا! آپ پر سلام ہو اے حجتِ خدا آپ پر سلام ہو اے زمین کی تاریکیوں میں خدا کے نور سلام ہوآپ پر اے وہ جن کی شان خدا نے ظاہر فرمائی آپ کی زیارت کو آیا ہوں آپ کے حق سے واقف آپ کے دشمنوں کا دشمن آپ کے دوستوں کا دوست پس میری شفاعت کریں اپنے رب کے حضور اے میرے آقا۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA WALIYYAL-LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA HUJJA-TALLAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA NOORAL-LAAHE FEE ZOLO-MAATIL ARZE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA MAN BADAA LILLAAHE FEE SHAANE-HI ATAY-TOKA ZA-AA'e RAN A’ARE-FAN BE-HAQQE-KA MO-A’ADE-YAN LE-A’DAAA'e KA MO-WAALE-YAN LE-AWLE-YAAA'e KA FASFA’ (ASHFA’) LEE I’NDA RABBEKA YAA MAWLAA-YA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا وَلِيَّ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا حُجَّةَ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا نُوْرَ اللهِ فِيْ ظُلُمَاتِ الْاَرْضِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا مَنْ بَدَا لِلهِ فِيْ شَاْنِهٖ اَتَيْتُكَ زَاۗئِرًا عَارِفًا بِحَقِّكَ مُعَادِيًا لِاَعْدَاۗئِكَ مُوَالِيًا لِاَوْلِيَاۗئِكَ فَاشْفَعْ (اشْفَعْ) لِيْ عِنْدَ رَبِّكَ يَا مَوْلَايَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicT