d, al-Shahid, and Muhammad ibn al-Mashhadi have said the following: When visiting the two Imams (a) together, you may say the following words after you stop at the holy tomb…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaikh Mufid, Shahid aur Muhammad ibne Mashhadi ne farmaaya hai keh: Jab tum dono Imam (a) ko mukhaatib karo to unki qabro’n ke saamne khade ho kar is tarah se unki ziyarat padho’n…", "UrduDescription": "امام موسیٰ کاظمؑ اور امام محمد تقی ؑ کی مشترک زیارتیں دو ہیں: ان میں سے ایک وہ ہے جو ان دونوں میں سے ہر امام کے لئے علیٰحدہ پڑھی جاتی ہے چنانچہ شیخ قولویہ قمی ؒنے کامل الزیارات میں امام علی نقی ؑ سے روایت کی ہے کہ ان دونوں ائمہ میں سے ہر ایک کی زیارت اس طرح پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014045, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on both of you, o the representative of Allah. Peace be on both of you, o the decisive arguments of Allah. Peace be on both of you, o the lights of Allah in the darkness of the (ignorant) world. I bear witness that, verily, you had successfully carried and delivered that for which Allah had commissioned you, protected that which was entrusted to you, prescribed that which Allah has made lawful, made clear the divine rules, studied and interpreted the Book of Allah, while directing affairs in the light of the divine rules, exercised self-control bravely in the midst of offensive provocations, till the inevitable came unto you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho aap dono par ay Auliya Allah. Salaam ho aap dono par ay Hujjat’e Khuda. Salaam ho aap dono par keh aap zameen ki taarikiyo’n mein do (2) noor hai. Mai gawahi deta hu, keh aap dono ne Khuda ka paighaam pohonchaya jo aap ko mila, aap ne hifaazat ki uski jo aap ko diya gaya. Aap ne halaale Khuda ko halaal bataaya, haraame Khuda ko haraam kaha. Aap dono ne Khuda ki hudood jaari ki. Aap dono Qur’an ki tilaawat karte rahe aur aap dono ne Khuda ki khaatir masaaeb aur aziyyat par sabr kiya hosh-mandi se, yahan tak keh shaheed ho gaye.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو آپ دونوں پر اے اولیاء اﷲ!سلام ہو آپ دونوں پر اے حجت ِخدا سلام ہو آپ دونوں پر کہ آپ زمین کی تاریکیوں میں دو نور ہیں میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ آپ دونوں نے خدا کا پیغام پہنچایا جو آپ کو ملا آپ نے حفاظت کی اس کی جو آپ کو دیا گیا آپ نے حلال ِخدا کو حلال بتایا حرام ِخدا کو حرام کہاآپ دونوں نے حدودِ خدا جاری کیں آپ دونوں قرآن کی تلاوت کرتے رہے اور آپ دونوں نے خدا کی خاطر مصائب اور اذیت پر صبر کیا ہوش مندی سے یہاں تک کہ شہید ہوگئے۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAYKOMAA YAA WALIYYAL LAAHE AS-SALAAMO A’LAYKOMA YAA HUJJATAYIL LAAHE AS-SALAAMO A’LAYKOMAA YAA NOORAYIL LAAHE FEE ZOLOMAATIL ARZE ASH-HADO ANNAKOMAA QAD BALLAGH-TOMAA A’NIL LAAHE MAA HAMMALAKOMAA WA HAFIZTOMAA MAS-TOO-DEA’TOMAA WA HALLALTOMAA HALAALAL LAAHE WA HARRAMA HARAAMAL LAAHE WA AQAMTOMAA HODOODAL LAAHE WA TALAWTOMAA KETAABAL LAAHE WA SABARTOMAA A’LAL AZAA FEE JAMBIL LAAHE MOHTASEBAYNE HATTAA ATAAKOMAL YAQEENO.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمَا یَا وَلِیَّیِ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمَا یَا حُجَّتَیِ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمَا یَا نُورَیِ اللہِ فِیْ ظُلُمَاتِ الْاَرْضِ۔ اَشْھَدُ اَنَّكُمَا قَدْ بَلَّغْتُمَا عَنِ اللہِ مَا حَمَّلَكُمَا وَحَفِظْتُمَا مَا اسْتُوْدِعْتُمَا وَحَلَّلْتُمَا حَلَالَ اللہِ وَحَرَّمْتُمَا حَرَامَ اللہِ وَاَقَمْتُمَا حُدُوْدَ اللہِ وَتَلَوْتُمَا كِتَابَ اللہِ وَصَبَرْتُمَا عَلَی الْاَذٰی فِیْ جَنْبِ اللہِ مُحْتَسِبَیْنِ حَتّٰی اَتٰیكُمَا الْیَقِیْنُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014046, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I turn to Allah by disconnecting all links with your enemies. I seek nearness to Allah through my love for you, I have come near you, fully aware of your rights, attached to your friends averse to your enemies, well acquainted with the guidance you adhered to, mindful of the depravity of your opponents. So speak on my behalf before your Lord, because, verily, your grandeur, before Allah, is the most exalted, your position is highly celebrated.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai Khuda ke saamne aap ke dushmano se be-zaari karta hu aur aap se mohabbat ke zariye Khuda ka qurb chahata hu, aap ki ziyarat ko aaya hu aap ke haq se waaqif, aap dono ke dosto’n ka dost, aap dono ke dushmano ka dushman, us hidaayat ko samajhta hu jis par aap dono qaaem hai, aap dono ke mukhaalif ki gumraahi ko jaanta hu. Pas aap dono meri shafa’at kare apne Rab se, keh aap dono ka Khuda ke yahan bada martaba aur behtareen maqaam hai.", "Urdu": "میں خدا کے سامنے آپ کے دشمنوں سے بیزاری کرتا ہوں اور آپ سے محبت کے ذریعے خداکی قربت چاہتا ہوں آپ کی زیارت کو آیا ہوں آپ کے حق سے واقف آپ دونوں کے دوستوں کا دوست آپ دونوں کے دشمنوں کا دشمن اس ہدایت کو سمجھتاہوں جس پر آپ دونوں قائم ہیں آپ دونوں کے مخالف کی گمراہی کو جانتا ہوں پس آپ دونوں میری شفاعت کریں اپنے رب سے کہ آپ دونوں کا خدا کے ہاں بڑا مرتبہ اور بہترین مقام ہے۔", "RArabic": "ABRA-O ELAL LAAHE MIN A-A’DAAA-EKOMAA WA ATAQARRABO ELAL LAAHE BE-WELAAYATEKOMAA ATAYTOKOMAA ZAAA-ERAN A’AREFAN BE-HAQQEKOMAA MOWAALEYAN LE-AWLEYAAA-EKOMAA MO-A’ADEYAN LE-A-A’DAAA-EKOMAA MUSTABSERAM BIL-HODAAL LAZEE ANTOMAA A’LAIHE A’AREFAN BE-ZALAALATE MAN KHAALAFAKOMAA FASH-FA-A’A LEE I’NDA RABBEKOMAA FA-INNA LAKOMAA I’NDAL LAAHE JAAHAN A’ZEEMAN WA MAQAAMAM MAHMOODAN.", "ArabicText1": "اَبْرَءُ اِلَی اللہِ مِنْ اَعْدَآئِكُمَا وَاَتَقَرَّبُ اِلَی اللہِ بِوِلَایَتِكُمَا اَتَیْتُكُمَا زَآئِرًا عَارِفًا بِحَقِّكُمَا مُوَالِیًا لِاَوْلِیَآئِكُمَا مُعَادِیًا لِاَعْدَآئِكُمَا مُسْتَبْصِرًۢا بِالْھُدَی الَّذِیْ اَنْتُمَا عَلَیْهِ عَارِفًا بِضَلَالَۃِ مَنْ خَالَفَكُمَا فَاشْفَعَا لِیْ عِنْدَ رَبِّكُمَا فَاِنَّ لَكُمَا عِنْدَ اللہِ جَاھًا عَظِیْمًا وَمَقَامًا مَّحْمُوْدًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014047, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "Now kiss the grave and go to the head side and recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ab qabre mubarak ko bosa de aur phir sar ki jaanib khade ho kar is tarah se kahe…", "UrduDescription": "اس کے بعد ان قبور مبارکہ پر بوسہ دے۔ اپنا دایاں رخسار ان پر رکھے اور پھر سرہانے کی طرف جاکر یہ پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicB